items.entry: Last few days I've been working on my own website.I've learned html,css,js, and react. Today, I learned that Github lets you host your own project websites for free, and how to use react-router to make a SPA.

I learned how to use fetch to get data in a remote database today. I was thinking about implementing a blog entry where anyone can post an entry but for security reasons I wont be doing that. I want to post memes in ... memes and I don't know if I need an about section.
